the various components of hadoop 1x are
hdfs
mapreduce
Master node
Slave node
hdfs
it is the file system used by hadoop 1x it is distributed file system
mapreduce
map reduce is a java program which runs in hadoop 
it consist of a mapper which split data into key value pair
and reducer which reduces the mapper out put
in between there is shuffel and sort which sort and suffle all the output of mapper
the master node consist of 
job tracker 
name node

job tracker
it is used to assign ap reduce to task tracker
name node 
it contrals the data nodes check for its avaiablity for space and name spaces

slavve nodes are connectedd to the master node consist of data nodes and task tracker
the task tracker performs mapreduce on datta nodes in slave machine
data nodes consist of large amount of data stored as blocks
